            <p class="muted" style="font-size: 20px;text-align: justify;">We acknowledge that the London Police Service is on the traditional territory of the Anishinaabek, Haudenosaunee, Lūnaapéewak and Attawandaron Nations, on lands connected with many treaties such as the Dish with One Spoon Covenant Wampum. <br><br>

